        <lb n="8"/>kūtta-p-perumāḷ poṟ-paṭṭam kuṭiñaikkallāl kaḻañcu U<hi rend="grantha">mā-bha</hi>ṭṭāraki poṟṟāli kāl Iṭaikkaṭṭu munṟun tāḷimpa<unclear>m</unclear> Iraṇṭu Iṭṭa muṭṭin pañ
